Young people everywhere are taught the supposed certainty of evolution. What are the fruits of such a teaching?

Suicide is the leading killer of teenagers. Is there perhaps a relationship between the teaching of evolution and the high suicide rate we find among teens?

This presentation shows the benefits of worshiping the God who created the heavens and the earth.
